Class Point2DExtAdapter

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.controllers.gsonCtrl.JsonAdapters.Point2DExtAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.google.gson.JsonDeserializer<Point2DExt>, com.google.gson.JsonSerializer<Point2DExt>
public class Point2DExtAdapter extends Object implements com.google.gson.JsonSerializer<Point2DExt>, com.google.gson.JsonDeserializer<Point2DExt>
Custom GSON adapter for serializing and deserializing Point2DExt objects.

Implements JsonSerializer and JsonDeserializer to handle the conversion between Point2DExt and JSON.
